init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So when one of the elders was called to a meeting by a shadowy figure, he couldn't say no.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He found that the spectre was of course the alien leader.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The shadowy figure offered to help the elder's tribe in finding the source if they would help them in their fight against the remaining humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The elder decided he couldn't trust the aliens and tried to get away but the shadowed figure caught him in time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The elder's daughter Nia was a strong-willed, brave young woman.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After the aliens were defeated, the elders of the remaining tribes made plans to form their own government where they would use the source for good.
